Clix is an independent, non-commercial fan clone inspired by Jawbreaker, the
Windows Mobile puzzle game (SameGame family). For context on the original
title, see:
https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Jawbreaker_(Windows_Mobile_game)

"Jawbreaker", "Bubble Breaker", Windows Mobile, and related names may be
trademarks of their respective owners. This project is not affiliated with,
endorsed by, or sponsored by Microsoft, Oopdreams software, Inc., or any other
rights holder of the original games.

Clix was implemented by Mili Hunjic at age 21 (c. 2006).
